  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink31-kilavi"> muṉṉorunāḷ taṉṉōṭu putuppuṉalāṭuḻi, ‘iṉip puṟattoḻukkam virumpēṉ’ eṉa
          āyattārōṭu cūḷuṟṟa talaimakaṉ piṉpum parattaiyarōṭu puṉalāṭat toṭaṅkukiṉṟāṉ eṉpatu kēṭṭa
          talaimakaḷ avaṉuḻaiyar kēṭpat tōḻikkuc colliyatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink31">
          <l> amma vāḻi tōḻi makiḻnaṉ</l>
          <l> kaṭaṉaṉ ṟeṉṉuṅ kollō nammūr </l>
          <l> muṭamutir marutattup peruntuṟai</l>
          <l> yuṭaṉā ṭāyamō ṭuṟṟa cūḷē.</l>

        </lg>
        <lg xml:lang="en">
         <l> Alas, friend!</l> 
         <l>Does the oath that we, when bathing together with [our] girlfriends, were witness to</l>
         <l>at the big ghat of crooked mature myrobalan trees</l>
         <l>in our village, say, “There is no virtue</l> 
         <l>in the delightful man”?</l> 



        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
  </text>
